name: Threedy illustrations
description:
Hello, threedy is an open source project.

~ and we will update it regularly


-> Visit threedy buymeacoffee page for exclusive illustrations


We just want to share. And hopefully someone will be helped by this project.


We actually wanted this project to help you create the illustration part of your UI design. But you could also use it anywhere.


Don't forget to mention us, so that this project could be better known and help more people.


And to our supporter, monthly and yearly members, we thank you for keeping this project alive. We have a gift for you, which is the rendered image of an illustration with its environment every time we finish making an illustration for threedy.


sincerely,

threedy designers
